    impact: "Its impact is on long-running autonomy patterns. It solves four problems that block unattended agent execution: getting stuck (graduated escalation), forgetting instructions (protocol fingerprint checks), losing cross-session knowledge (lessons protocol), and wasting iterations on infeasible approaches (environment-aware hypothesis filtering). The two-phase interaction boundary — wizard setup then fully autonomous — makes overnight runs practical.",
